<div
  class="box"
  style="
    background-image: url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1719179513227-15758bc779ed?q=80&w=1856&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D);
  "
>
  <div class="hero-2">
    <h1>Explore Some Of Our Featured Herbs</h1>
    <div class="featured-plants">
      <% for (let i = 0; i < 8; i++) { %>
      <div class="featured-plant">plant <%- i+1 %></div>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    <a href="#" class="btn hero-2-btn" type="button"
      >Discover More &nbsp;<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i
    ></a>
  </div>
</div>
<div
  class="box"
  style="
    background-image: url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1719702702556-43c793e2b625?q=80&w=1856&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D);
  "
>
  <div class="hero-3">
    <div class="hero-3-left">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519389950473-47ba0277781c?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D"
        alt=""
      />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-3-right">
      <h1>About The Project</h1>
      <p>
        The Virtual Herbal Garden is a digital sanctuary that brings the ancient
        wisdom of herbal medicine into the modern world. This immersive platform
        allows users to explore a rich collection of medicinal plants, each
        meticulously detailed with its botanical characteristics, healing
        properties, and traditional uses. Whether you're a student,
        practitioner, or simply an enthusiast of natural remedies, the Virtual
        Herbal Garden offers an educational and engaging experience that makes
        the knowledge of herbal medicine accessible to all.
      </p>

      <p>
        At the heart of the Virtual Herbal Garden lies an array of interactive
        features designed to enhance your learning journey. Users can explore
        realistic 3D models of plants, delve into comprehensive multimedia
        content, and embark on guided virtual tours that highlight specific
        themes like digestive health, immunity, and skincare. By combining the
        power of technology with the age-old practices of herbal healing, the
        Virtual Herbal Garden provides a unique opportunity to connect with
        nature and discover the therapeutic benefits of plants from the comfort
        of your home.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
